  "common": {
    "name": {
      "zh": "B-11 AKS-74U护木",
      "en": "AKS-74U Zenit B-11 handguard"
    },
    "shortName": {
      "zh": "B-11",
      "en": "B-11"
    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "以铝合金D16T为原料一体化量产的B-11护木，经过了黑色涂层处理。能够替代AKS-74U的标准护木。在握把的两侧安装有皮卡汀尼导轨，可以在此基础上安装额外的配件（战术握把、手电筒、激光指示器等）。",
      "en": "The integrally machined B-11 foregrip is manufactured from aluminum alloy D16T with black coating and can be installed instead of the standard-issue foregrip on the AKS-74U. The foregrip is fitted with Picatinny rail mounts on three sides, allowing for the installation of additional equipment such as tactical foregrips, flashlights, and laser designators. Manufactured by Zenit."
    },
